text: Eduard Anatoliyevich Suboch () (born 11 May 1969) is a Soviet ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1988 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:People from Chernogorsk Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Ski jumpers at the 1988 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Khakassia
